Self-critique:
On page 36 Mitsumori says「よろしくしねえ」in response to Misaki's statement「彼女ちゃんにもよろしくね」. It should be a flat "No." instead of a "Kill yourself".
The reason I used the latter is because I misread the line initially as「よろしくし(死)ね 」, which means "fuck you" (literally, 'die').
By the time I had noticed, I had typeset the page and I found the line far too funny to remove, even as an error.
